beer.beer_description: With a crisp, clean, base beer inspired by a Kolsch SIx String have used a little improv and uplifted the mofo with blood orange juice and vanilla, amalgamating the traditional with the amplified! The blood orange’s deep red blush gives a red hue along with a sweet citrusy flavour and zesty bitterness. The El Dorado and Hallertau hops compliment the citrus and the distinct sweetness of the vanilla adds a balance that ties together this unique beer.
